# ClaudeCoach root crontab (sanitised reference / rebuild template)
#
# SECURITY: the CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN is NOT stored inline here. Each job is
# run through /root/.claude/cc-run, which sources /root/.claude/cc.env (chmod
# 600, root:root) to inject the token into the job environment at run time.
# cc.env is the same EnvironmentFile the systemd bots use. Never paste the
# token value into this file or into the crontab.
#
# Rebuild on a fresh box:
#   1. create /root/.claude/cc.env  ->  CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=sk-ant-oat01-...
#      chmod 600 /root/.claude/cc.env
#   2. install /root/.claude/cc-run (see ClaudeCoach/system/cc-run), chmod 700
#   3. crontab ClaudeCoach/system/crontab.template
#
0 20 * * 0 /root/.claude/cc-run bash /Users/diamondpeakconsulting/diamondpeak-site/ClaudeCoach/scripts/weekly-summary.sh
